@graph.name: Go4me.ai
@graph.description: The world's first digital-to-physical agent service. AI-powered field agents (gophers) complete real-world tasks on your behalf.

@graph.name: Go4me.ai Agent Service
@graph.description: On-demand field agents complete real-world tasks including In-N-Out delivery, DMV proxy services, dry cleaning pickup, lost and found recovery, location monitoring, and custom errands.

itemOffered.name: In-N-Out Delivery
itemOffered.description: Order In-N-Out Burger delivered to your location by a vetted field agent. Menu selection, payment, and delivery handled for you.

itemOffered.name: DMV Proxy Service
itemOffered.description: Send a field agent to the DMV or government office on your behalf. Handle registration, renewals, and paperwork without waiting in line.

itemOffered.name: Eyes On Location Monitoring
itemOffered.description: Have an agent visit a specific location to provide live updates, photos, and status reports. Perfect for property checks, construction monitoring, or verification.

itemOffered.name: Lost and Found Recovery
itemOffered.description: Get help locating and reclaiming lost items from businesses, venues, or public spaces. Agents coordinate with locations and retrieve your belongings.

itemOffered.name: Dry Cleaning Pickup and Delivery
itemOffered.description: Have dry cleaning picked up from your location and retrieved from the cleaners when ready. Convenient laundry service without leaving home.

itemOffered.name: Custom Errand Service
itemOffered.description: Request any legal task or errand. Our field agents handle custom requests from document delivery to retail returns and more.

acceptedAnswer.text: Go4me.ai connects you with vetted local agents (we call them gophers) who complete real-world tasks on your behalf. Simply describe your task, and we'll dispatch an agent to handle it. You get SMS updates and photo/receipt proof when it's done.

mainEntity.name: Can I get In-N-Out delivered in San Diego?

acceptedAnswer.text: Yes! Go4me.ai offers In-N-Out Burger delivery in San Diego. Our agents pick up your order and deliver it fresh to your location. Simply place your order through our app.

mainEntity.name: Can someone go to the DMV for me?

acceptedAnswer.text: Yes! Our DMV Proxy service allows you to send a vetted agent to the DMV or government office on your behalf. They can handle registration renewals, paperwork submission, and other DMV tasks as your authorized representative.
We're currently live in San Diego. Los Angeles and San Francisco are launching within 2 weeks. Join our waitlist to be notified when we launch in your city.
